aheed Uddham Singh]]''\n| MovieBox Birmingham Ltd|MovieBox\n| [[Sukshinder Shinda]] \n|}\n\n===Singles===\n{| class=wikitable\n|-\n! Year\n! Song\n! Record label\n! Music\n! Notes\n|-\n| 2013\n|Feem (Cut Like A Diamond)\n|Replay Music/ [[Sony Music India]]\n|Partners in Rhyme\n|Single\n|-\n| 2014\n|Rise Above Hate\n|Jazzy B Records/[[MTV]] Spoken Word Production\n|[[Millind Gaba]]\n|[[Panasonic Mobile]]\n|-\n| 2015\n| Singhan Di Talwar\n| Jazzy B Records\n| Beat Minister\n|\n|-\n| 2015\n|Most Wanted ft. [[Mr. Capone-E]] & [[Snoop Dogg]]\n|Jazzy B Records/[[MTV]] Spoken Word Production\n|Ji-Madz EWC\n|First Time Collaborating\n|-\n|2015\n|Repeat\n|Speed Records\n|[[JSL Singh]]\n|Lyrics: Balkar Nandghria\n|-\n|2016\n|Attwaadi ft Kaur B\n|Speed Records\n|[[Dr. Zeus]]\n|Lyrics: Raj Ranjodh\n|-\n|2016\n|Leap Wala Saal\n|Speed Records\n|[[DJ Flow]]\n|Lyrics: Veet Baljit\n|-\n|2016\n|Dynamite\n|[[Moviesbox]]\n|[[Dr. Zeus]]\n|[[Roach Killa]]\n|-\n|2016\n|Trendster\n||Speed Records\n|[[Deep Jandu]]\n|[[Gangis Khan]]\n|-\n|2017\n|Manke To Manak\n|Jazzy B Records\n|[[Sukshinder Shinda]]\n|Nav Garhiwala\n|-\n|2017\n|Bamb Gaana\n|Jazzy B Records\n|[[Harj Nagra]]\n|Lyrics: Gursewak Dhillon\n|-\n|2017\n|Shaheed Kaum De\n|Jazzy B Records\n|Ranjha Yaar\n|Jung Sandhu\n|-\n|2018\n|One Million\n|Speed Records\n|[[Dj Flow]]\n|Lyrics: Singga\n|-\n|2018\n|90 Di Bandook\n|Jazzy B Records\n|[[Harj Nagra]]\n|Lyrics: [[Karan Aujla]]\n|-\n|2018\n|Miss Karda\n|[[T-Series (company)|T-Series]]\n|[[Kuwar Virk]]\n|Lyrics: Kuwar Virk\n|-\n|2019\n| Udhne Sapoliye\n|[[Planet Recordz]]\n|[[Jassi Bros]]\n|Lyrics: [[Satti Khokhewalia]]\n|-\n|2019\n| Maa Boli\n|[[Jazzy B Recordz]]\n|[[Aman Hayer]]\n|Lyrics: [[Ninder Moranwalia ]]\n|-\n|2019\n| Khande To Khalsa\n|[[Jazzy B Recordz]]\n|[[Jassi Bros]]\n|Lyrics: [[Sandhey Sukhbir]]\n|-\n|2019\n| Worldwide\n|[[Jazzy B Recordz]]\n|[[Harj Nagra]]\n|Lyrics: [[Ninder Moranwalia]]\n|-\n|2019\n| Dhan Dhan Baba Nanak\n|[[Jass Records]]\n|[[Jassi Bros]]\n|Lyrics: [[Satti Khokhewalia]]\n|-\n|2019\n| Aaja\n|[[Jazzy B Records]]\n|[[Jassi Bros]]\n|Lyrics: [[Kaddon Wala Jeet]]\n|-\n|2020\n| All Eyez On Me\n|[[Sony Music India]]\n|[[Roach Killa]]\n|Lyrics: GV, Lally Mundi\n|}\n\n===Duo collaborations===\n{| class=wikitable\n|-\n! Year\n! Work\n! Label\n! Notes\n|-\n|2019 \n| Dil Mangdi\n|Speed Records\n|[[Sukh-E]], [[Apache Indian]], [[Jaani (songwriter)|Jaani]]\n|-\n|2018\n|Jatt Da Flag\n|[[T-Series (company)|T-Series]]\n|With Kaur B & [[Tru-Skool]]; Lyrics: Amrit Bova\n|-\n|2016\n|Shikaar\n|Speed Records\n|Preet Hundal,With [[Kaur B]] & [[Amrit Maan]]\n|-\n| 2014\n| ''Collaborations 3''\n| MovieBox Birmingham Ltd|MovieBox\n| With [[Sukshinder Shinda]] (duo collaboration)\n|-\n| 2014 \n| ''Mitran De Boot'' (single)\n| Jazzy B Records & Speed Records\n| With Kaur B & [[Dr. Zeus]]\n|-\n| 2014\n| ''Singhan Diyan Gadiyan'' (single)\n| MovieBox Birmingham Ltd|MovieBox/Speed Records\n| With [[Popsy The Music Machine]] \n|-\n| 2013\n| ''The Holi War''\n| Benaras Media Works\n| With [[Bappi Lahiri]] \n|-\n| 2012\n| ''The Folk King \u2013 A Tribute To Kuldip Manak'' \n| MovieBox Birmingham Ltd|MovieBox\n| With [[Aman Hayer]] \n|-\n| 2012\n| ''This Party Gettin' Hot'' (single)\n| Jazzy B Records/[[Speed Records (record label)|Speed Records]]\n| With [[Yo Yo Honey Singh]]\n|-\n| 2010\n| ''Naag 2 \u2013 Hyper''\n| Kamlee Records Ltd/[[Speed Records (record label)|Speed Records]]/Planet Recordz\n| With [[Popsy The Music Machine]] (duo collaboration)\n|-\n| 2009\n| ''Satguru Mera''\n| MovieBox Birmingham Ltd|MovieBox/StarMakers/[[Music Waves]] \n| With [[Sukhshinder Shinda]] (duo collaboration on tracks 2, 4, 6 & 9)\n|-\n| 2009\n| ''Collaborations 2''\n| Planet Recordz\n| With [[Sukhshinder Shinda]] (duo collaboration)\n|-\n| 2008\n| ''Chargai Sohniye''\n| Genie Records/[[Speed Records (record label)|Speed Records]]/Planet Recordz\n| With [[Aman Hayer]] and DJ Kendall (duo collaboration)\n|-\n| 2006\n| ''Collaborations''\n| Planet Recordz\n| With 